{"tid":1636591,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［整合］有Pc仔細佬想紅 有冇人幫下佢","createTime":"2019-10-07T18:46:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T03:36:47.000Z","uid":312155,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"b0e1c995f7e373f6c960bc8caa34216b5f6aca7b","tid":1636591,"uid":312155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T18:46:27.000Z","msg":"事源係Pc仔個細佬係Ig上面Po咗個咁嘅Story<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o6ObnAL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo6ObnAL.jpg&h=1ad14ea8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然細佬即刻比眾多巴絲糾正返佢啦<br />\n然後Pc仔就為咗幫細佬出咗以下Story<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4xA1KRC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4xA1KRC.png&h=a560e76a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cWpqr4Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcWpqr4Y.png&h=7c88074c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YfVJdKZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYfVJdKZ.png&h=a8e4e5c1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gyKxRwF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgyKxRwF.png&h=3f937c08&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k8WTAYk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk8WTAYk.png&h=14300c3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其後有巴打爆出細佬以前原來都好憎狗㗎，點知啊哥做咗狗之後就轉咗做藍屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />女朋友仲要係大陸人，果然黑警中共一家親<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CZeaDc2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCZeaDc2.png&h=32d223e0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A7ZNFro.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA7ZNFro.png&h=98d7ef11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/chPByPk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FchPByPk.png&h=cbbfb6ec&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VRe9TPm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVRe9TPm.png&h=f4a90278&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yCw00un.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyCw00un.png&h=034398ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n已知細佬叫周浩天<br />\nIg:cht_pudding<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dq6PTN8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDq6PTN8.png&h=64799982&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n啊哥(狗)叫周浩賢<br />\nIg:peaceyinusone<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3Dszktr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Dszktr.png&h=a7c48454&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎各位巴絲留言作出補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光後香港 時代革命<br />\n黑警死全家"},{"pid":"5d8800113aae7053006b298be6cdcdbd41be794c","tid":1636591,"uid":312155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T18:47:31.000Z","msg":"自推1/10"},{"pid":"26cb5f315594e733791c9cb0608825031c3af94d","tid":1636591,"uid":312155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T18:47:46.000Z","msg":"自推2/10"},{"pid":"74bc72d8433d1f1114eaf5abeee6957a24c3da19","tid":1636591,"uid":312155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T18:47:59.000Z","msg":"自推3/10"},{"pid":"3d8cea5064db4f3c602a24e757b3d255d7c20147","tid":1636591,"uid":81336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T18:48:15.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d9e76b959257950eb3cb043e9a67c215f0a74c49","tid":1636591,"uid":312155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T18:49:09.000Z","msg":"自推4/10"},{"pid":"325c79bcf57e8af6e44050ca9135d01c0b10b58f","tid":1636591,"uid":312155,"like":0,"dis